Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.58,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:22.57,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.17,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:34.01,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,The flight... Papa's flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:40.36,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Do you really think you'll be able to kill Yin when you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.83,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She's just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.81,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Why did you save her the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:00.10,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I have a lead. They're trying to get far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.47,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:08.18,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Does your power always have to be so extravagant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.53,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Aren't spectacles fascinating?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.79,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It's more like La traviata than it is Aida.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.39,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.12,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll explain it to you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:20.25,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,All particles vibrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:25.95,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,so when I hit them with their vibrational frequency, they'll begin to resonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:31.04,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,In other words, the vibration is amplified to the point of destruction. Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:32.40,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:36.13,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,In any case, that's what my ability is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:39.01,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,That's why I can destroy any object I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.31,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,even the most obscure of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:51.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the original chestnut glutton rice, harvest rice kokeshi doll, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.62,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Boss, lend me some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.49,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,We also need to buy something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:59.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're on the job, you know. What are you going to do if you get drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.26,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,No problem! I fall asleep whenever I get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.20,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, that's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.63,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to go home, Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:15.82,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy about going back to your homeland?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.68,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.87,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.17,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:24.00,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi, how do I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.66,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You're not the same person I once knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:34.33,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I heard there were many people who became like you after a certain point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:38.77,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Your emotions seem unstable... Yes, you must be ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.69,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.93,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Go back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.93,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.29,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.33,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I'm not go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.82,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I tried to find you whenever I was on tour abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.48,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.48,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.78,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Mr. Kastinen, about the money for our expenses... Can you cast it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.41,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I knew you were going to say that. That wasn't even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.38,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Look at the guy next to the cop who's inspecting everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.95,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,He's trying to trace the connection I'm transmitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.53,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Are they looking for contractors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.94,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Cut the line already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.11,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It's already been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.86,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It might have been a little too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.57,DTB-Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.78,DTB-Default,Cop B,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.79,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Was that one of your abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.08,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,An unimpressive one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.78,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I made his heart vibrate sympathetically, which made it come to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:01.09,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,My remuneration won't change, regardless of whether it's spectacular or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.85,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We only know that much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm continuously receiving information from our superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.18,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Can you find out where she is at any time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.69,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.48,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It means that no one can escape the grasp of the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:21.50,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,If people like you weren't associated with us, you'd probably be a bunch of serial killers or renegades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:24.67,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Be grateful you're on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:27.85,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,My ass is on the line, so hurry up and go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.11,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,How's the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.14,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Still broken. There needs to be water nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.09,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,That's a tough remuneration you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.84,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, it doesn't have to be cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:53.69,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Anything will do, as long as I put it inside my mouth and spit it back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.70,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It's a habit from your days as a human, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.50,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It looks like luck's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.39,DTB-Default,Stationmaster,0,0,0,,We will be stopping to allow the oncoming train to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.00,DTB-Default,Stationmaster,0,0,0,,The delay will be approximately five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.42,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi, are you sure someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.54,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,They're coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, where are those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:43.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Now isn't the time to be sleeping! You could have at least watched over them while I was using the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.10,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Damn. We're getting off at the next station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.22,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Come on. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.33,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,No, you can't touch me there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:55.41,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,What are you taking pictures of? That could be considered voyeurism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.99,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:24.22,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I'm going to find something to burn. Wait inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.13,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.40,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Fourteen A Heart Unswaying on the Water's Surface... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.40,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:02.19,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I had a daughter in the past. An infant baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.49,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Her father was a creep. I broke up with him shortly after she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.05,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,She was unbelievably adorable,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.52,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,just like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:19.50,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Even though I was a singer, I was a heavy smoker. Sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.03,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I stopped smoking while she was in my womb,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.15,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,but I should have stopped for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.52,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I carelessly left a cigarette somewhere within her grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:33.96,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,She put it inside her mouth. Before I realized it, she had already choked to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.41,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It was so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:45.83,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I wept for the next several nights. Before I knew it, the night sky had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.37,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Why did you save her the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.73,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.36,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.77,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.24,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You were thinking about that night, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:52.36,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I think I know why you don't want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:57.84,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You have sad memories of your homeland, which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.12,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.14,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.12,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Isn't that what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.61,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.70,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The sadness, as well as everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.71,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I remember it. I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:25.64,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,If I didn't run outside that day, Mama wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.27,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.71,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Ever since that night, it disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.60,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The silver light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:41.09,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,"Bearing the sins of the children of Earth, the moon begins to consume its light."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.16,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Which poem is that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.67,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.65,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It might have been a stanza from an aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.42,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,They say that a lunar eclipse is a symbol of atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:56.86,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,In that case, the moon must be in a perpetual state of atonement, since it can't be seen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.86,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,You're a strange contractor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.87,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:11.17,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything going on between your mother and me at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:15.06,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You noticed it after all, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:19.53,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,The feelings I always kept inside of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:26.03,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Guilty thoughts about stealing your mother away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.95,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you... I wanted to tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.41,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel guilty about it, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.50,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,W-Who the hell are you? You look suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.98,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Wait! I swear I've seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That's right. I saw you at the construction site when it collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:01.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you the stalker who's after the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.26,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.26,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,This is something you shouldn't be involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What did you say? Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.64,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What did you do to that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.27,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,She's really quiet and doesn't show many expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.65,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's like she's some kind of doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.15,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.13,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:26.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Even if it doesn't show in her expressions or her words, she's crying within her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.16,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:31.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There isn't a single person in this world that deserves to be treated like a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.17,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.58,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.87,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,All the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.57,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.01,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.41,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.58,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you take Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:17.17,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Yin? Are you talking about Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.54,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,What are you people up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.38,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.01,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.59,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.85,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Did you run away on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.27,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.06,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I thought my soul would be able to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.49,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Is she being chased because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.28,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Are you her partner in crime or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.63,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.78,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.93,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:55.58,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.33,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.81,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,He's the one from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.95,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do? Is collecting information still our top priority?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.45,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Leave the doll. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.37,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:07.58,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I see... You defibrillated your own heart with electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.17,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Bertha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:20.75,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm through with you, Yin. You're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.36,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Itzhak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:02.16,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,What kind of light is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.16,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I can't see anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.98,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:11.20,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.72,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Bertha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:20.85,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Maiden, black night, mourning in sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:25.50,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,falling into the night alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:31.01,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,The moon that accompanies her radiates of silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:36.53,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,as the night of atonement quietly passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.14,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,That wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.47,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.18,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Dolls can't shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.80,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.47,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Cold sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.46,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.43,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,I heard you ran into trouble with a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:31.94,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:37.46,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't make an issue out of this since there wasn't any harm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:42.20,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,It's been assumed that the contractors you disposed of were from the FSB.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.15,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,If they had received the information, you'd already be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.54,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.21,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Turn in the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.53,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,It'll be reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:18:01.87,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,No, I've only started to get the feel of using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.88,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.11,DTB-Default,Owner,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:09.47,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Don't let your emotions get the best of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.89,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Emotions? Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Kastinen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.86,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,There was no doubt it was him, so I tried to start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.48,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,He looked at me as if he never saw me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.80,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It might have been his way of saying you should forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.91,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,He's probably worried that it might become a well-known scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:46.83,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,He looked strange, as if his memory was erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.28,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.84,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Kirsi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:58.23,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Right. She was back at the tobacco shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.43,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Did those two not get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:04.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, there's no point in prying into a private matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:11.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,We received our payment, and you even went to the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.34,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have much of a choice after you deserted me, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:17.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You didn't have a choice? Any reasonable person would have come back after finding out they've been deserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.45,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Well, everyone was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:21.45,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.42,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Let's go back, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.59,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Let's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.19,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to be caught up in your past anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.30,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.81,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Am I your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.76,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.30,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,It's up to you to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.02,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,whether you want to remain here as Yin or be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:52.95,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.44,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.38,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Let's go back, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.81,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.44,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.14,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:13.25,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.51,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Are you okay with this, Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.64,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The sun shines a somber glitter as the hag sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:50.96,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The recurring destruction is a requiem for the lost past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.17,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Is the remuneration for betrayal blood or tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.55,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The chain reaction of indignation has started and cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:04.54,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The town is full of chaos and dissonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.26,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Fifteen Memories of Betrayal in an Amber Smile... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.26,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The stage has been set.